scenes.description: Guests (Council/Promise members) complimenting IRyS on her performance of 'Shangri-La'.
IRyS introduces a game to test her acting skills.
IRyS talks about Japanese food (sushi and green tea) while waiting for the props.
IRyS and guests cast a magic spell to make the sushi appear.
The sushi appears on the table, and IRyS introduces the tuna and squid sushi.
IRyS explains the rules: one sushi has wasabi, and she will pretend both do.
IRyS eats the tuna (maguro) sushi and acts out a reaction.
IRyS eats the squid (ika) sushi and performs another reaction.
The guests guess which sushi had the wasabi.
The correct answer is revealed, and IRyS reacts to the lingering spice.
IRyS offers the guests a pose request as a reward for guessing correctly.
